  ## 10. Cross-Slice Error Code Contract

  Define and enforce these deterministic codes (example set; finalize exact names once schema is implemented):

  1. BILLING_DEPENDENCY_CONFLICT
  2. ENTITLEMENT_DEFINITION_IN_USE
  3. PLAN_IN_USE
  4. PRODUCT_IN_USE
  5. PAYMENT_METHOD_NOT_FOUND
  6. PAYMENT_METHOD_NOT_OWNED_BY_ENTITY
  7. PAYMENT_METHOD_PROVIDER_UNSUPPORTED
  8. PURCHASE_NOT_FOUND
  9. PURCHASE_REFUND_NOT_ALLOWED
  10. PURCHASE_VOID_NOT_ALLOWED
  11. PURCHASE_ADJUSTMENT_DUPLICATE
  12. PLAN_ASSIGNMENT_NOT_FOUND
  13. SUBSCRIPTION_NOT_FOUND
  14. PROVIDER_OPERATION_NOT_SUPPORTED

